snippet.title: Kingpin: Life of Crime - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Disclaimer: The soundtrack is a part of the game and therefore is licenced by Sony Music for game developer.

Official trailer of Kingpin PC game featuring Cypress Hill's 'We Ain't Goin' Out Like That' released somewhere in late 1998 by Xatrix Entertainment.
